description:
Company introduction
Founded in 2018, Nexus FrontierTech envisions to be at the forefront of the wave to introduce intelligent data management into the business, transforming the workplace to become smarter and more productive,  enabling employees to use their talents in more creative work. 
Our Intelligent Automation solutions have been helping renowned institutions and companies across industries to digitize their data, either structured or unstructured, leading to a significant reduction of manual data workload.
Having raised $3.8 million in seed funding, we are now poised to further our R&D and growth activities to expand our product offerings beyond document processing. 
With new projects coming, we’re looking for 02 Backend Engineers to lead the development, from the requirements to deliverables.
Tasks & Responsibilities: You’ll be entrusted to:
Consult the Project Manager and the clients on the technical topics, ensuring the best performance, quality, and responsiveness of the application;
Design and deliver the applications/functions with well-structured and formatted code complying with the company’s code standards;
Resolve any obstacles and bugs coming in the way to the final deliverables;
Deliver reports on a regular basis and on request;
Build up the installation guidelines accordingly;
Propose and execute the initiatives to grow the technical team as well as to exceed client’s expectations;
Collaborate with a global project team of members in the UK, Singapore, Japan, and Vietnam to deliver the project smoothly.

experience:
Background experience & hard skills:
Professional experience of minimum of 3 years with PHP;
Professional experience of minimum of 2 years with Laravel;
Knowledge in database programming or design skills, including relational database skills (SQL, Postgres, etc.) having non-relational database skills (MongoDB, Redis, Cassandra, etc.);
Knowledge in CI/CD (Jenkins, CircleCI) and knowledge in E2E testing (Detox, NightWatch,…);
Experience in working with globally-based clients and teammates;
Experience with other coding languages (i.e Python, ReactJS) is a plus point
Exposure to AI (either academic knowledge or professional experience) is a huge plus point.
Soft skills:
Communication skill: smooth in Vietnamese and intermediate in English
Independent learning and research skill
Problem-solving skills

Personal qualities:
Self-motivated;
Excited to deal with ambiguity and overcome difficulties;
Interested in new technologies, especially AI;
Committed to delivering the best possible result and to the project timelines;

