description:
Netpower Vietnam has vacant positions for Fresher/Junior QC/QA (Tester) located at our Vietnam office to join our ever-expanding product team. You will join an existing international team of great people and will have a chance to contribute to a great success story while learning and growing with us.
Primary responsibilities including but not limited to:
Analyze and understand business and technical requirements and work with the project managers, the product owner in our HSEQ product;
Collaborate in the developer to test developed modules in a structured and successful way;
Develop, execute and review test cases based on functional, technical and usability requirements;
Create, execute and review test cases on functional and non-functional requirements;
Manage and report on your own test deliverables and test execution;
Create and manage defects along with evaluating severity and impact on the solution and scope;
Take responsibility for certifying the quality of the solution;
Plan and organize your own work and accurately report issues and progress in a timely manner;
Identify areas for own personal development
Report testing status and test results to superior (Project Leader or direct manager) accurately and in timely manner
Daily scrum meeting;

experience:
Required qualifications are as follows:
03 months + of software testing experience in developing, reporting software issues, report testing status and results;
Critical thinking and domain research & studying is important;
Have a basic knowledge of testing methodologies & techniques and the defect reporting process;
Able to understand well documents in English (here are test requirements or system specifications) to collect requirements for TCs development;
Shows initiative in gaining in-depth experience in areas of technology relevant to testing of given software products. Shows initiative in gaining theoretical knowledge in software testing;
Candidate must be an enthusiastic and energetic person. He/she must be efficient, hardworking, team working and able to use good judgment;
Problem solving, issue escalation skill and time management skill;
Good communication skill (expression);
Good at all 4 English skills;

